        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-51e9d58e-206b-4be4-b56a-51566ae87ec4">
                Lieut.-Colonel Lipton
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-51e9d58e-206b-4be4-b56a-51566ae87ec4" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1947-01-22/debates/0a11e28a-2905-4e9f-8575-2464e8eb4742/Deserters(SurrenderCall)#contribution-51e9d58e-206b-4be4-b56a-51566ae87ec4">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">asked the Minister of Defence whether he will make an announcement arising from the review by the Service Departments of the problem of deserters.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-51e9d58e-206b-4be4-b56a-51566ae87ec4" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
