<p class="">I will, with permission, make a statement at the end of Questions in reply to these Questions.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-aa320dd6-acd4-43fa-988f-eb8c25ebad1f" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
